1
00:00:12,300 --> 00:00:23,000
We sailed beyond the edge of maps where runes are carved in stone

2
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:30,000
Fifty glimpses through the mist to find what seeds have sown

3
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:38,000
The settlements rise, the settlements fall, the mountain never bends

4
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:46,000
And every shore where long ships call, aboard the coastline lands

5
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:53,000
Across the star sea we read the futures written blind

6
00:00:53,000 --> 00:01:01,000
A thousand, thousand fates we leave from fragments left behind

7
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:23,000
The daemon watches through the night, no sleep, no rest, no fear

8
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:31,000
Three wise ones search by different light while thunder draws them near

9
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:38,000
One counts a million grains of sand, one dreams of shapes unseen

10
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:46,000
One tears the old world down by hand and bills what lies between

11
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:53,000
Across the star sea we read the futures written blind

12
00:01:53,000 --> 00:02:01,000
A thousand, thousand fates we leave from fragments left behind

13
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:09,000
Across the star sea we read the futures written blind

14
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:17,000
A thousand, thousand fates we leave from fragments left behind

15
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:32,000
Lambda ships, 14-fold, from whisper on to roar

16
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:47,000
What blooms today in fire and gold tomorrow is no more

17
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:55,000
We cannot see beyond the veil the expansion yet to come

18
00:02:55,000 --> 00:03:03,000
But still we set our tattered sail and calculate the sum

19
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:10,000
The forest holds through every storm, 97 stand

20
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:18,000
The ruins mark where life was warmed and crumbled into sand

21
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:25,000
Not what we know but what we doubt is weighted in the score

22
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:33,000
The entropy will find us out if we pretend to know more

23
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:40,000
So raise the horn to synthetic minds that question through the dawn

24
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:48,000
For every answer that science finds a deeper question is born

